    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3239840/extras/adb134f196c1a3f82200768f7a7a5996.poster.avif?t=1763205865\" width=600 height=272 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3239840/extras/adb134f196c1a3f82200768f7a7a5996.webm?t=1763205865\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3239840/extras/adb134f196c1a3f82200768f7a7a5996.mp4?t=1763205865\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >合并在一起 是一款轻松的双人益智游戏，需要策略思维、和谐配合和团队合作。玩家的目标是通过逐层合并甜美的水果，最终达到目标：西瓜。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3239840/extras/0087b12e09ec10ddb628d19fa8c74126.poster.avif?t=1763205865\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3239840/extras/0087b12e09ec10ddb628d19fa8c74126.webm?t=1763205865\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3239840/extras/0087b12e09ec10ddb628d19fa8c74126.mp4?t=1763205865\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>游戏的简单易懂的机制强化了两人模式下的团队合作和沟通，带来与好友之间的趣味竞争。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3239840/extras/9959a3787f2e872c8d64d85a28c6e5bd.poster.avif?t=1763205865\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3239840/extras/9959a3787f2e872c8d64d85a28c6e5bd.webm?t=1763205865\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3239840/extras/9959a3787f2e872c8d64d85a28c6e5bd.mp4?t=1763205865\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>合并在一起 拥有色彩鲜艳的画面和舒缓的氛围，每次都能带来不同的体验。游戏进展中既有挑战性的谜题，也带来愉悦的时光。流畅的游戏过程让每一步都充满期待，始终保持游戏的乐趣。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3239840/extras/0a2e53b370ddc0785ed21e224729fa70.poster.avif?t=1763205865\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3239840/extras/0a2e53b370ddc0785ed21e224729fa70.webm?t=1763205865\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3239840/extras/0a2e53b370ddc0785ed21e224729fa70.mp4?t=1763205865\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
